Interface OConstants

All Known Subinterfaces:
AllValuesFromRestriction, AnonymousClass, CardinalityRestriction, HasValueRestriction, MaxCardinalityRestriction, MinCardinalityRestriction, OClass, Restriction, SomeValuesFromRestriction
public interface OConstants

This interface holds some constants used by several other intrfaces and classes in the GATE ontology API.

Author:
Niraj Aswani, Johann Petrak
